import bisect_driver
import shlex
import sys

def ExpandArgs(args, target):
	for arg in args:
		if arg[0] == '@':
			with open(arg[1:], 'rb') as f:
				ExpandArgs(shlex.split(f.read()), target)
		else:
			target.append(arg)
	return target

stage = sys.argv[1]
dir = sys.argv[2]
execargs = ExpandArgs(sys.argv[3:], [])

sys.exit(bisect_driver.bisect_driver(stage, dir, execargs))
